 merged into 'Who Lucy Is'\",\n          \"'Lucy In One Sentence' — redundant with profile\",\n          \"Duplicate Resource entries (Claw Code, OpenTrader, Screenshotlayer, TradingAgents, Vibiz)\",\n          \"Rafael Telegram bot token (security — shouldn't be in memory)\"\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775444417427}}
