link is ongoing but still relevant\n\n**Files to archive:** Check for files older than 90 days (before Jan 6, 2026) — none exist, oldest is Mar 8.\n\nNow let me apply the consolidation:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_WQ7uy62Ez0k8Ai8OVkC8b2","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","edits":[{"oldText":"> Last consolidated: 2026-04-05 03:00 UTC (auto-dream)","newText":"> Last consolidated: 2026-04-06 03:00 UTC (auto-dream)"},{"oldText":"- **30-Day Sprint (Mar 8 – Apr 5):** Today is the deadline day. No bookkeeper validation has started yet. Gabriel & Raguel haven't done real outreach. Focus shifted to infrastructure, MAGI, and Sentra work during the sprint.","newText":"- **30-Day Sprint (Mar 8 – Apr 5):** Sprint ended Apr 5 with zero bookkeeper validation. Focus shifted entirely to infrastructure, MAGI, and Sentra work. Gabriel & Raguel haven't done real outreach. DataFlow validation still needs to happen — timeline TBD."},{"oldText":"## MAGI v2 Features\n- Chat, Roundtable (turn-based, persists to disk), Mission Control, Analytics, Files, Settings\n- IT Support page (emergency controls, model management, diagnostics)\n- WhatsApp Allowlist Manager, Message Forwarding Rules\n- Personal Knowledge Base (/magi2/knowledge/)\n- Mini Roundtable (on-demand/scheduled/smart trigger)\n- Voice Call page (WebSocket, hold-to-talk, agent selector)\n- Login: lucy/lucy2026","newText":"## MAGI v2 Features\n- Chat, Roundtable (turn-based, persists to disk), Mission Control, Analytics, Files, Settings\n- IT Support page (emergency controls, model management, diagnostics, quick commands)\n- WhatsApp Allowlist Manager, Message Forwarding Rules\n- Personal Knowledge Base (/magi2/knowledge/)\n- Mini Roundtable (on-demand/scheduled/smart trigger)\n- Voice Call page (WebSocket, hold-to-talk, agent selector)\n- **User Management** (/users/): register flow, admin approve/reject, role management (Admin/User), admin-only endpoint protection\n- **Design System (Apr 5)